The '''Evil Eye''', also known as the '''EYE''', is an enemy in ''[[Final Fantasy]]''. It is encountered as a miniboss in the [[Cavern of Ice]] guarding the [[Levistone]], and in the [[Flying Fortress]] as a [[random encounter]].

